summary: My angel turns 38 today. I could write a whole novel about how much I love you and how you saved my life but I thought I’d keep...
body: My angel turns 38 today. I could write a whole novel about how much I love you and how you saved my life but I thought I’d keep this short and simply. Happy birthday, Tom. You’re the love of my life, you’re the light of my life, you’re my happiness. I love you so much and I could never be able to thank you enough for everything you’ve done. I can’t imagine a life without you. Thank you for coming into my life and and be the best part of it. You’re my entire world ❤️

summary: who do you guys think was speaking during the latest endgame trailer?
body:
who do you guys think was speaking during the latest endgame trailer?

many say ultron is the one saying “not us” at the very end, but eh idk?? the beginning lines sound like tony and steve, not just one person, to me personally.

also do you guys think they photoshopped people out certain scenes? i can go off at this, but i wanna see your thoughts and theories.
